      "message": "consider this scenario:  you install this chart, create schema = true. it creates a schema.\n\nWith this annotation, a change to any of the 7 configmaps will cause this job to restart itself (I am not 100% whether this applies to jobs or just deployments/pods).  There is no user intervention to set the create schema flag to false because it is all automatic. I think the job will run again and fail cause the schema already exists..",
